> [!NOTE]
> **Design Decision — Dropdown vs Free Text for Role:**
> Using a dropdown (select) instead of a free-text input ensures role names are consistent with the Curriculum Planner agent's expectations. The options map directly to the SOP categories we've created (Engineering, Compliance, Finance, IT, General). This prevents the user from typing "SWE" or "dev" which might confuse the Planner.

